    <div>
      <strong>Here are some of the basic and advance but important tips to bring <span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/sitelinks/" title="查看sitelinks中的全部文章" target="_blank">sitelinks</a></span> for your site:</strong>
    </div>
    
    <p>
      <strong>以下是为你的网站带来网站链接的一些基本和高级但是重要的贴士：</strong>
    </p>
    
    <ol>
      <li>
        <strong>SEO is Important:</strong> Your blog / site should have optimized title, description and keywords Meta tags. If you own a <span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/wordpress/" title="查看WordPress中的全部文章" target="_blank">WordPress</a></span> blog, you can try <a title="All-in-one-SEO-pack" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/" target="_blank"><strong>All-in-one-SEO-pack</strong></a> but basis <strong>search engine optimization</strong> is required for every site.搜索引擎优化是重要的：你的博客或者网站应该有优化了的标题、描述以及关键词元标签。如果你有一个<span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/wordpress/" title="查看WordPress中的全部文章" target="_blank">WordPress</a></span>博客，那么可以试一下<a title="All-in-one-SEO-pack" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/" target="_blank"><strong>All-in-one-SEO-pack</strong></a>这个插件，但是基本的搜索引擎优化对每个网站都是需要的。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Remove Broken Links:</strong> Make your website error free by removing the 404 / error links.移除死链：通过移除404错误的链接确保你的网站没有错误。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Number of WebPages: </strong>Unless your website / blog have some articles it is impossible to get <span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/sitelinks/" title="查看sitelinks中的全部文章" target="_blank">sitelinks</a></span>. Your blog should have at-least 20-25 WebPages.网页数量：除非你的网站或博客有一些文章，不然获得网站链接是不可能的。你的博客应该有至少20到25个页面。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Internal Linking:</strong> The best way to bring sitelnks is interlinking. Interlink your important WebPages from different other WebPages (which you want to think in <span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/sitelinks/" title="查看sitelinks中的全部文章" target="_blank">sitelinks</a></span>). It also helps from users and usability perspective to increase page views and users stay time.内部链接：带来网站链接的最好办法是内链。从其他不同的网页链接指向你的重要页面（这些可能是你想出现在网站链接中的）。这样还可以在用户和使用的角度增加页面浏览次数和访客停留时间。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Good and Simple Navigation: </strong>Your blog should have good and simple navigation system. Try to have a <ul> and <li> list of links at the top for your blog. Put the navigation links in these tags. They also consider title tags of the pages.好而简单的导航：你的博客应该有好而简单的导航系统。尝试在博客顶部使用<ul>和<li>标记的链接列表。把导航链接放入这些标签。谷歌也会考虑这些页面的标题标签。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Search Engines Traffic: </strong>If you get lot of traffic from search engines your blog will surely get familiar and it will be easy for getting sitelinks. Your blog should have High click through rates.搜索引擎流量：如果你从搜索引擎获得大量的流量，你的博客肯定会被谷歌蜘蛛熟悉并且获得网站链接也会容易些。你的博客应该有高的点击率。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Searches and Clicks: </strong>The number of searches and the no. of clicks that your blog gets for a certain keyword will also be considered for sitelinks. Your blog should also get many clicks for the searched keyword.搜索和点击数量：你的博客在某些关键词获得的搜索和点击数量也将被考虑。你的博客还应该获得很多被搜索词的点击。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Flow of Traffic: </strong>Your WebPages should have a consistent flow of traffic to get Google Sitelinks. If the traffic sources are from Search Engines, you should be more than happy.流量流动：你的网友应该有一个持续的流量以获得谷歌网站链接。如果这些流量来自于搜索引擎，那么你应该倍感高兴。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Blog’s Age:</strong> It<strong> </strong>was time when you need to wait for a year or so to get one or multi-line sitelinks. Now-a-days, Google can assign sitelinks to your site within 4-5 months, those WebPages should be high relevant to their users.博客年龄：是时候你需要等待一年或者更长以获得单行或多行的网站链接了。如今，谷歌可能会在四到五个月内给你生成网站链接，这些网页应该与其用户高度相关。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Quality Content:</strong> Content is the king<strong> </strong>and it’ll provide you the targeted traffic so update your blog with quality content on a regular basis.优质内容：内容为王，而且优质内容还会给你提供目标流量，因此用优质的内容有规律地更新博客吧。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Link Bait: </strong>If you write a quality article copy, then you’ll get the advantage of link bait.链接诱饵：如果你写高质量的文章，那么你将获得链接诱饵的优势。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Sitemap:</strong> Create an error free<strong> sitemap</strong>, include all the links in the sitemap. Make sure to submit the sitemap in Google webmaster tool.网站地图，创建一个无错误的网站地图，其中包含所有的链接。确保在谷歌<span class='wp_keywordlink_affiliate'><a href="https://xiaoq.in/tag/%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e7%ae%a1%e7%90%86%e5%91%98%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7/" title="查看网站管理员工具中的全部文章" target="_blank">网站管理员工具</a></span>中提交站点地图。
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Reconsider Your Site: </strong>If you didn’t get sitelinks even after applying above mentioned tips, then you should request Google to reconsider your site. You have this option in Google Webmaster Tools.重新审核你的网站：如果你符合上述贴士中的要求之后还是没有获得网站链接，那么你应该要求谷歌重新审核你的网站。
      </li>
    </ol>
    
